Auron veers sharply upward to avoid the missle like darts that 
daydreamer fired at him. As he look down towards the new person about 
to fight him and Daydream he smiled and thought. If I could take both 
of them out I wonder.... his thoughts went on in this form. He 
shouted out loud "Ahahahha fools, ahahaha" he laughed with 
vengence. "Now it is time to meet your makers. As he said this his 
wings faned back suddenly. The sun bright in the distance was covered 
up with his wide outspread. below them a huge shadow fell where his 
opponents were standing. Auron holds out his hands to both sides of 
his body. He begins to quiver as little slits in his wings begin to 
open up. As you look up Aurons eyes begin glowering red and his body 
seems to shimmer in the morning daylight. "Yes are you ready now" as 
he says this his sensors lock on his foes below. As his arms come 
together, he smiles a crazy demented smile. "Lock" he says as his 
hordes of missles come out of his wings are in fiering postion. As 
they come out it seems he has volleys and volleys of them 
stored. "Are you ready now" he asked once more as the first volley 
came down, 20 missles locked on Daydreamer and his new opponent went 
streaming toward them.
